ntum which can be released upon a\ncessation of shape changes. This work demonstrates how the interaction between\nenvironmental curvature, active driving and geometric phases yields rich,\nexotic phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 17 Dec 2021 19:51:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 19 Jan 2022 22:59:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-18"}
