s much\nas 31.74% improvement in inference accuracy and 71.07% reduction in scaling\nenergy consumptions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 18 Dec 2021 06:04:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-21"}
